ng coins or for assassinating other players. Just don't get killed by your own creations!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435750/extras/2e7e13794cb178aea2a4f7ac2a7d20ef.avif?t=1750337117\" width=613 height=152 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435750/extras/3ee9aa5b769514f574561da93267c625.avif?t=1750337117\" width=616 height=459 /></span></li></ul>",
